    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "calling it \"a necessary evil\" seems pretty subjective though. If the mining causes permanent ecosystem destruction or massive pollution in certain areas, how can we say it's actually better for the planet overall? Isn't \"greener\" just a political label if the damage is just being moved from one place to another?",
